description:
This course is gives in depth explanations and solutions to a sample PSLE from 2007 .  The solutions are presented step by step with voice overs and graphics to help you understand the principals involved.  

The sections correspond to the two papers and two books in the PSLE.  You can get through the entire exam in less than 90 minutes. Review each question with solution as often as you want.

Unlike a tuition centre, you can learn anytime and anywhere as long as you have a computer, tablet, or smartphone and an internet connection.  Learn at home with friends and family.  Learn at your own pace.  Pause at anytime to discuss amongst yourselves or ask a parent (or nearby adult).
title: Singapore P6 Math Aug-2007 prelim problems w/solutions
